analysis_result.summary: The rental agreement is for Flat No. 302, Rose Residency, located in Baner, Pune, owned by Mr. Rajesh Sharma. The tenant, Ms. Priya Nair, is a software engineer at Infosys Pune with a permanent address in Kochi, Kerala. The monthly rent is INR 25,000 plus a maintenance charge of INR 2,000. A security deposit of INR 75,000 (cheque no. 128756 dated 01/03/2025) is required. The agreement is valid for 11 months, from 1st March 2025 to 31st January 2026. Mr. Sanjay Kulkarni from Baner, Pune, and Mrs. Ritu Deshmukh from Kothrud, Pune, act as witnesses.
